=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>1</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>Here again ‘resurrected’ readings have passed, the second already. This time it was passed… It was passed because\nraining. Instead of readings, it turned out to be a flat on Mayakovsky Square with his monument in the rain.</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 604px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8546eb190a6179840869d23ad68a9836/efa6e/Xjw762gOpyQ.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/8546eb190a6179840869d23ad68a9836/23ddf/Xjw762gOpyQ.avif 604w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 604px) 100vw, 604px\"\n              type=\"image/avif\"\n            /><source\n              srcset=\"/static/8546eb190a6179840869d23ad68a9836/059a8/Xjw762gOpyQ.webp 604w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 604px) 100vw, 604px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/8546eb190a6179840869d23ad68a9836/efa6e/Xjw762gOpyQ.jpg 604w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 604px) 100vw, 604px\"\n            type=\"image/jpeg\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/8546eb190a6179840869d23ad68a9836/efa6e/Xjw762gOpyQ.jpg\"\n            alt=\"2\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\"><p>2</p></figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>I think that in such a case, the organizers need to carry a bust of Mayakovsky in their pockets, place it where\nconditions are more comfortable, and conduct readings there (an alternative meeting point in case of bad weather). The\nidea of grading the best is good, but I immediately thought: ‘What about the worst? They also need to be celebrated’.\nThis time everyone could hearable and that, of course, was awesome! That’s the reason why I didn’t like all the readers\nat the first event: I couldn’t hear them.</p>\n<p>Still, such an event should be more numerous.</p>\n<p>Update: The worst readers should be given Dontsova’s book.</p>","id":"5ff2499d-b9d8-5186-ae6b-6d9d5f28bc51"},"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"ITFarrier"}}},"pageContext":{"langKey":"en","language":"en","next":{"fields":{"langKey":"en","slug":"/en/blog/2016-07-17-tatyshev-island-festival/"},"frontmatter":{"language":null,"title":"Tatyshev island festival","type":"post"}},"previous":{"fields":{"langKey":"en","slug":"/en/blog/2016-05-28-bard-ring/"},"frontmatter":{"language":null,"title":"Bard‐ring","type":"post"}},"slug":"/en/blog/2016-05-30-mayakovsky-readings/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2674376943","357539041","4035578580"],"slicesMap":{}}